Cell[TextData[StyleBox["As you can see, after conjugation, the position of \
the letter will go to arbitrary position, but we will still require in the \
ansatz we constructed, these new letters appears in the last two entries, \
this is why the constraints are so strong for svmpl",
 FontSize->18,
 FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0.5, 0]]], "Text",
